{"type":"message","id":"ee18b0c5","parentId":"5d9511fe","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:42:23.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a very interesting document! It's a career planning / immigration planning document for someone with a background in Mechanical Engineering (bachelor) + Software Engineering (master), 5 years of programming experience, with IELTS 6, French A1, and a budget of 200,000 (presumably RMB or CNY).\n\nThe document outlines 5 different immigration/career change plans:\n1. Canada BAS (Building Automation Systems) - Commissioning Technician\n2. Ireland Mechatronics - Engineering Visa\n3. New Zealand Green List\n4. Australia Regional 482/491 (Mining Automation)\n5. Quebec PEQ/QSTP (French-based)\n\nLet me summarize this for the user in Chinese since they sent the document in Chinese and seem to be Chinese-speaking.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"文档已解析！这是一份**海外职业移民规划方案**，针对你这样的情况：\n\n## 📋 个人背景\n- **学历**：机械本科 + 软件硕士\n- **工作经验**：5年程序开发\n- **语言**：雅思6分、法语A1\n- **预算**：20万\n\n---\n\n## 🗺️ 五套差异化方案\n\n| 方案 | 目标国家 | 核心思路 |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| **方案一** | 加拿大 BAS | 楼宇自动化调试技术员，双学位最对口，薪资高、移民稳 |\n| **方案二** | 爱尔兰 | 机电一体化工程师，落地快、全英语、程序员经验可直接用 |\n| **方案三** | 新西兰 | 绿名单直通车，软件/机械技术员，一步到位、环境好 |\n| **方案四** | 澳洲偏远地区 | 矿山自动化，高薪+5天8小时，但地理孤立 |\n| **方案五** | 魁北克 PEQ | 法语兴趣结合，技术音频设计师，但政策有波动 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 核心逻辑\n利用**双学位**进行职业套利，利用**英语/法语**寻找低分赛道。\n\n---\n\n你想深入了解哪个方案的**第一步**该怎么走？或者需要帮你评估具体起薪？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":688,"output":423,"cacheRead":32765,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33876,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140134802}}
