{"type":"message","id":"a68b5c22","parentId":"0b4b47f2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:42:28.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to compare another AI (Gemini)方案 with the ones we just analyzed. But I don't have the Gemini方案 yet - the user said \"另外一个ai gemini 给了一个方案我贴给你看下\" but hasn't actually pasted it yet. \n\nI should ask the user to share/paste the Gemini方案 so I can compare and evaluate it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好呀，把 Gemini 给你的方案贴过来吧～ 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":3186,"output":92,"cacheRead":30717,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33995,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140144326}}
