{"type":"message","id":"ee8d2cb1","parentId":"fae5c920","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:42:54.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the document I just parsed is actually the Gemini方案. So the document I already analyzed is the Gemini proposal. Let me re-read it and compare it with our original 5 proposals to do a comprehensive evaluation.\n\nFrom what I extracted, the Gemini方案 has 5 options:\n1. 加拿大 BAS 楼宇自动化\n2. 爱尔兰\"机电一体化\"工签\n3. 新西兰\"绿名单\"直通车\n4. 澳洲\"偏远地区\"482/491\n5. 魁北克 PEQ/QSTP\n\nBut wait - the user said this document IS the Gemini方案, and they're asking me to compare it with \"我们之前的方案\" (our previous proposals). \n\nLooking back at the conversation, the document I just parsed seems to be what the user shared - but this appears to BE the Gemini proposal. The user said \"另外一个ai gemini 给了一个方案我贴给你看下\" - meaning this document is the Gemini one.\n\nSo I think the user might be confused, or perhaps they had previous proposals from me that I'm not aware of. Let me ask for clarification - do they have another document with \"our\" previous proposals, or should I interpret this as comparing these 5 options against each other?\n\nActually wait - I should check my memory to see if there are any previous proposals documented.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我刚才解析的就是你发来的 Gemini 方案，里面有5个选项：\n\n| 方案 | 国家 | 职业 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 一 | 加拿大 | BAS楼宇自动化调试技术员 |\n| 二 | 爱尔兰 | 机电一体化工程师 |\n| 三 | 新西兰 | 软件程序员/机械技术员 |\n| 四 | 澳洲偏远地区 | 矿山自动化 |\n| 五 | 魁北克 | 技术音频设计师 |\n\n---\n\n你提到\"和我们之前的方案\"对比——你是指之前在其他地方(比如之前跟某AI或顾问聊过)给过的方案吗？如果有的话，把那个方案也发给我，我来做综合评估和排序 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":428,"output":417,"cacheRead":33789,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34634,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774140165487}}
