{"type":"message","id":"e077fed7","parentId":"fdde29f0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T00:44:25.738Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o2bs2irmhxj3_1","toolName":"feishu_search_doc_wiki","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"total\": 15,\n  \"has_more\": false,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T09:13:39+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-21T20:05:26+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"ZhCAd4Nk5o5do4xqRfTcuRUhnNf\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-20T23:16:50+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/docx/ZhCAd4Nk5o5do4xqRfTcuRUhnNf\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"<b>转行</b><hb>移民方案</hb><b>终极评估与建议</b>   🇨🇦 <h>加拿大</h>\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"转行<h>移民方案</h>评估与建议 - yuriy\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-03-20T09:46:07+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-20T22:33:00+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"FLhQwhSBniU56tkzVjbc2JD6nHg\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-03-20T23:17:56+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/FLhQwhSBniU56tkzVjbc2JD6nHg\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"<b>转行</b><hb>移民方案</hb><b> - 多路径并行策略</b>   - <h>移民</h>国家：<h>加拿大</h>/澳大利亚/新西兰\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"转行<h>移民方案</h>终极评估与建议\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-18T23:49:41+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"FILE\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-20T08:56:46+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"TuzPwkxMtid95HkHD9PcweujnBf\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-01-18T23:49:41+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/TuzPwkxMtid95HkHD9PcweujnBf\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"...发展全<h>方案</h> 一、核心规划逻辑 国内集中冲刺法语  四、PR获批后：登陆<h>加拿大</h>双线发展<h>方案</h>（无缝衔接） （一）电工+暖通双...\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>加拿大</h>法语EE规划：国内拿PR+登陆双线发展全<h>方案</h> (1).docx\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"DOC\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-16T17:46:26+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"is_cross_tenant\": false,\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-01-17T06:41:37+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"IE6Hdu6WcoeTuOxuYFqci1n3nGh\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-01-16T17:46:26+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/docx/IE6Hdu6WcoeTuOxuYFqci1n3nGh\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"<h>加拿大</h>PR实操全流程指南（适配IT背景法语<h>移民</h>，主备路径双<h>方案</h>）\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>加拿大</h>PR实操全流程指南（适配IT背景法语<h>移民</h>，主备路径双<h>方案</h>）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-07T10:06:08+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-20T08:56:33+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"ZlPwwjGKzi49VHk0KxHcB1bfnWd\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-01-07T12:20:19+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/ZlPwwjGKzi49VHk0KxHcB1bfnWd\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"我已将这份 34岁软件工程师 「<h>加拿大</h>先行，澳洲后续」两步走<h>移民</h>规划 整理为飞书文档专用纯文本格式，去除了所有格式标记，保留清晰的层级和表格，你可以直接全选复制，粘贴到飞书文档中，粘贴后格式会自动适配，无需额外调整。\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"1年语言学习+出国务工_<h>移民</h>完整规划文档（飞书适配版）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-16T17:27:52+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"FILE\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-01-16T17:29:22+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"BAsOwfgcBijHR2k27cJcVJwFn6e\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-01-16T17:27:53+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/BAsOwfgcBijHR2k27cJcVJwFn6e\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"...<h>移民</h>，主备路径双<h>方案</h>） 核心定位：结合你的  操作步骤：① 登录WES官网注册账户，选择“<h>加拿大移民</h>/公民申请”用途；② 按...\",\n      \"title_highlighted\": \"<h>加拿大</h>PR实操全流程指南（适配IT背景法语<h>移民</h>，主备路径双<h>方案</h>）.docx\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"entity_type\": \"WIKI\",\n      \"result_meta\": {\n        \"create_time\": \"2026-01-19T00:08:55+08:00\",\n        \"doc_types\": \"DOCX\",\n        \"edit_user_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"edit_user_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"last_open_time\": \"2026-03-20T09:00:18+08:00\",\n        \"owner_id\": \"ou_2458d9c0becde3ce8d02a3cc32a281de\",\n        \"owner_name\": \"yuriy\",\n        \"token\": \"IJMNwVuqyiziGekOJsEctKb3n1e\",\n        \"update_time\": \"2026-01-26T13:23:37+08:00\",\n        \"url\": \"https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/IJMNwVuqyiziGekOJsEctKb3n1e#DR98dJe1hoqhHOxyAJ5cHJW9nfc\"\n      },\n      \"summary_highlighted\": \"建议<h>方案